author: @rosemarwessels4157
content:
As a Brazilian I must say that was a beautiful gift to Rio de Janeiro’s people that make the concert a real party and enjoy to the most.
When a country and the world go through so much like a pandemic and a war, the people needs an warm hug and having fun is like be invited to a party, in this case Madonna’s party. It’s was awesome !
Check it out Rolling Stones in Rio, Copacabana beach. They did the same impact and unbelievable number of crowd.

CHEERS TO MADONNA AND PEOPLE FROM 🥂🥳🥂RIO DE JANEIRO✨✌️🫶✨😎✨🔆✨🕊️✨🎆✨JESUS CRISTO✨🙌
